name: "Shadow Spiral"
description:
This is a visual incantation.
Captured in a moment of deep inner focus, this photo radiates the vibrations of feminine power, resistance, and freedom.

The image is inspired by the myths of the Gorgon Medusa — she who stared fear in the face and turned it to stone.

This is not just a photograph. It is a symbol.

📷 One frame — one story.
🔮 One gaze — one challenge.
💠 This NFT is part of the Spirit Gorgons collection — a personal artistic journey through body, image, and magic.
